-- People’s Bank of China Will Cut Banks’s Reserve Ratio
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-05-12T11:18:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-12/people-s-bank-of-china-will-cut-banks-s-reserve-ratio.html
The People’s Bank of China said it is
cutting the reserve ratio requirement for banks by 50 basis
points starting from May 18, according to a statement on its
website today.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
Liza Lin in Shanghai at 
